本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:謝玉娟研究生(外文):Yu-chuan Hsieh論文名稱:NIKE贊助高中籃球聯賽之研究論文名稱(外文):A Sponsorship Study in the High School Basketball League- in the Case of Nike指導教授:彭小惠指導教授(外文):Hsiao-hwei Peng學位類別:碩士校院名稱:國立臺南大學系所名稱:體育學系碩士班學門:教育學門學類:專業科目教育學類論文出版年:2013畢業學年度:101語文別:中文論文頁數:80中文關鍵詞:質性研究、高中籃球聯賽、運動贊助外文關鍵詞:Qualitative research、HBL(High-school Basketball League)、Sport sponsorship相關次數:

被引用:3點閱:963評分:下載:246書目收藏:2



本研究為瞭解NIKE贊助HBL高中籃球聯賽之歷程，選擇NIKE運動行銷部經理及品牌行銷部經理進行深入訪談，研究目的主要為瞭解NIKE贊助HBL高中籃球聯賽的歷史背景；瞭解NIKE選擇贊助HBL的考量因素及動機；瞭解NIKE選擇贊助HBL的評估機制；瞭解NIKE歷年來贊助HBL的方式；以及瞭解NIKE未來持續贊助HBL的可能性。    本研究獲得結果如下：一、NIKE自1995年開始與高中體總配合辦理HBL高中聯賽到現在， 已經將HBL高中籃球聯賽深植許多年輕族群的心中，且HBL高中籃球聯賽是NIKE現在非常重視的一環。二、NIKE選擇贊助HBL的考量因素及動機為：有利於品牌形象的提升及認同、得到很理想的曝光率，以及增加市場調查及產品提升的便利性，另外給予禮遇機會是爲了能更進ㄧ步推廣籃球運動。三、NIKE選擇贊助HBL，無法在短時間內評估其贊助效益，僅能從長期賽會受到矚目的人口持續增加及透過賽會無價的廣告行銷方面做為願景效益評估。四、NIKE歷年來贊助HBL的方式為：財務、產品、師資培訓，和舉辦NIKE訓練營等。五、在台灣許多讀者、消費者，甚至球迷都把NIKE與HBL結合在一起，贊助HBL協助更多年輕籃球選手有更遠更好的舞臺，因此NIKE會持續贊助HBL。    根據研究發現與其對研究者的啟發，整理並提供相關單位團體與未來研究者做為參考。

To understand the procedure of NIKE sponsoring HBL(High-school Basketball League), the study interviewed the manager of Nike sports marketing department and the brand marketing manager. The purpose of this study is to understand the historical background, the way past sponsoring, and possibility in the future of NIKE sponsoring HBL. It will also examine what factors to consider, what motive, and what kind of estimate NIKE chooses to sponsor HBL.     The researcher comes to the findings as follows:1.  Nike has cooperated with Chinese Taipei School Sport Federation to help hold the HBL since 1995 and Nike has highly put emphasis on such an activity. In that way, HBL has deeply rooted in the young generation.2.  The consideration and motivation that Nike has chosen to sponsor HBL are such an activity helps Nike gain a sense of ownership and the opportunity of exposure. The sponsorship also helps increase the market investigation rate and promote the convenience of product usage. Furthermore, it helps increase the participation of basketball game.3.  For the long run, Nike can evaluate the effect of gain based on the grow of population participating in the HBL and the advertisement marketing during the ball games. The advertisement during the ball game can also bring benefits for the product marketing.4.  The ways Nike sponsoring HBL are financial support, products, teacher training and Nike training camps.5.  In Taiwan, many readers, consumers and even fans connect the image of Nike with HBL. Nike will continue to support HBL and through sponsorship, it helps to provide better stages for more basketball players.

